comments: O'Neale's (BKN) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim and is not released before the expiration of the shot clock.
Bridges (BKN) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball defending Doncic (DAL) on the perimeter.
Finney-Smith (BKN) establishes himself in Green's (DAL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Green (DAL) steps into Dinwiddie (BKN) and initiates body contact that affects his SQBR.
Dinwiddie (BKN) initiates contact with Green (DAL) and affects his FOM.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) briefly places a hand on Bridges (BKN) as he moves along the perimeter and the contact is marginal.
Green (DAL) establishes himself in O'Neale's (BKN) path and absorbs the contact.
Dinwiddie (BKN) straddles the lane line and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Green (DAL) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Finney-Smith (BKN) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Williams (DAL) commits a take foul on Thomas (BKN).
Bridges (BKN) establishes himself in Green's (DAL) path and is firming up as marginal contact occurs during the screen.
Finney-Smith (BKN) establishes himself in Williams' (DAL) path firming up and marginal contact occurs to WIlliams' shoulder as they disengage.
Kleber (DAL) and Finney-Smith (BKN) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Bridges (BKN) commits a take foul on Green (DAL).
Dinwiddie's (BKN) forward momentum carries him into Green (DAL), who has his forearm slightly extended, but the contact is marginal.
Dinwiddie (BKN) and Doncic (DAL) come together during the loose ball and the contact between the two players is incidental.
Replay review of the OOB called on Doncic (DAL)  pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Doncic is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Williams (DAL) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal lower body contact occurs with Bridges (BKN) after the release.
